{"id":393592,"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/icon.jpg","floor":"#1","group":"BUG 追踪","groupHref":"/group/issues","groupThumb":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/icon/m/000/00/04/433.jpg","message":"原因：bgm.tv的cookie有效期其实是1年，但开发把cookie破天荒的设置成了session模式，所以一旦退出浏览器cookie就会失效。<br><br>解决办法：安装 <a href=\"https://chromewebstore.google.com/detail/editthiscookie/fngmhnnpilhplaeedifhccceomclgfbg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow external noopener noreferrer\" class=\"l\">EditThisCookie</a> 扩展，在Bangumi网站内点击该扩展（图标类似&#x1F36A;），找到 <span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">chii_auth</span> 这个cookie，取消勾选 session 即可。<br><br><a href=\"https://ibb.co/KDXr5Jm\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow external noopener noreferrer\" class=\"l\"><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/VxtqLs3/chii.in.png\" class=\"code\" rel=\"noreferrer\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" alt></a>","time":"2024-2-12 12:13","title":"Bangumi网页版退出浏览器掉登录BUG的解决方法","userId":"855824","userName":"kikoeru","userSign":""}